entries.femaleVariant: Huh. Funny, was just thinkin' about you.
entries.maleVariant: Huh, funny. I was just thinkin' about you.

entries.femaleVariant: Got another job for me? Someone you need, y'know, taken care of?
Is it your, uh, uninvited guest? Things gotten worse?
Nothing like that. Actually, the opposite. Wanna get away from all that, cleanse.
It's... it's a little worse, yeah.
entries.maleVariant: It's, uh... it's a little worse, yeah.

entries.femaleVariant: Things've more or less stabilized. I'm-- We're getting used to each other.
entries.maleVariant: Think I'm more or less stabilized. I'm-- We're getting used to each other.

entries.femaleVariant: Hard to say, really.
OK, umm... Is this a date?
entries.maleVariant: OK. Uh... Is this a date?

entries.femaleVariant: Guess you'll have to find out. We'll have to.
Hm... You're not my type, girl. Just show up.
entries.maleVariant: Heh... You're not my type, holmes! Just show up.

entries.femaleVariant: Dam out past Rancho Coronado. Know it?
Shit... I'm so sorry…
Gotta hand it to you... Would've lost my shit, what, pff... ten minutes in, maybe.
Sure, what about it?
So, do I got amazin' timin' or are you always thinkin' about me?
S'all right. Haven't given up just yet.
Ooh, I know that voice, V. Are... are you OK?
Little, uh, abandoned bungalow lakeside. Meet me there – at sundown.
How do you plan to do that?
entries.maleVariant: Yeah, how do you plan to do that?

entries.femaleVariant: Y'know, I could be cursin' your name in my thoughts.
entries.maleVariant: Amazing? Y'know, I could be thinkin' and cursin' your name.

entries.femaleVariant: Hoh, hey... I'm just glad you remember me at all.
Ask to your heart's content.
Got a job for me?
A little bit.
Things've stabilized.
Hard to say.
Ask away. It's never boring with you.
Interesting people aren't easily bored.
Not in your company. OK, now that we've blown each other, what's up?
entries.maleVariant: No chance in your company. But now that we've blown each other, what's up?

entries.femaleVariant: Count me in.
Why the wetsuit?
All right then, count me in.
I'll see you there!
Aah, sounds fun, but I don't think I got the time right now.
entries.maleVariant: Ooh, sounds fun, but I don't think I got the time right now.

entries.femaleVariant: OK... is this a date?
See you there.
Don't have time, sorry.
That's it? No details?
Gotta say, I'm intrigued... Why the wetsuit?
entries.maleVariant: Gotta say, I am intrigued... Why the wetsuit?

entries.femaleVariant: Can't back out now. Just gonna have to use your imagination.
Really know how to reel me in, don'tcha?
entries.maleVariant: You really know how to reel me in, don't ya?

entries.femaleVariant: Ain't seen nothin' yet.
But I gotta warn you – I look great in a wetsuit.
entries.maleVariant: But I gotta warn ya – I look great in a wetsuit.

entries.femaleVariant: That sucks, heh... Well, lemme know if you change your mind.
It's not super urgent or anything.
That's it? No details? What's there to do out there?
Sorry, not gonna get me to spoil the surprise.
Trust me. You won't regret it.
Sounds like a plan. See ya there.
Buh-byyye!
He's definitely more present, but I guess I also got more... used to him?
Well, bet I got just the thing to take your mind off it.
Yeah... I won't pretend like I get that.
'Cause I got a favor to ask…
Hey, Jude. What's up?
Ah, you know, same ol'. You?
Got good days, got bad days. Same as ever.
entries.maleVariant: I got good days, got bad days. Same as ever.

entries.femaleVariant: Seen good days and bad days.
Been thinkin' about you.
You call just to see how I'm doin', or...?
entries.maleVariant: You, uh, call just to see how I'm doin', or...?

entries.femaleVariant: Not just. Got a favor to ask you…
See ya, V.
You're on a need-to-know basis. So, this particular mission don't require you to have no gun. Just a wetsuit.
Thought I'd never hear from you again.
Actually, thought I'd never hear from you again after... the Maiko sich.
entries.maleVariant: Actually, thought I'd never hear from you again after the... Maiko sich.

entries.femaleVariant: Rewatched the scroll from that day.
You had no choice.
But I ain't callin' to rehash old wounds. Got a favor to ask.
Believe it when I see it.
